"smart_blocks:cortex/parietal/inbox/2026/06/20/1158-session.md#Sessão Episódica: 2026-06-20 11:58#[feature] LLM Council Skill Implemented: The LLM Council skill has been implemented to enhance decision-making processes. This skill leverages a methodology adapted from Andrej Karpathy's LLM Council, employing five independent AI advisors. Each advisor approaches a query from a unique thinking lens: the Contrarian identifies flaws, the First Principles Thinker re-evaluates the core problem, the Expansionist seeks upside, and the Outsider offers an unbiased view. The skill is intended for complex questions where the cost of a wrong decision is high, providing a synthesized recommendation after peer review. It is triggered by phrases like \"council this\" or \"run the council\" and is not meant for simple factual lookups or basic creation tasks.": {"path":null,"last_embed":{"hash":"1bqlffk","at":1782088669631},"embeddings":{"TaylorAI/bge-micro-v2":{"vec":[-0.09987549,-0.00584197,0.03603953,-0.03431858,-0.03515295,0.01499796,0.01571218,0.02437254,0.03677187,-0.0623542,0.05947317,0.00855046,0.02605738,0.05380942,0.01766957,0.03913704,-0.04154263,0.02020321,0.05091209,0.0247884,0.06222364,-0.04012552,0.01756511,0.00734038,0.00871581,-0.0130252,-0.03603421,-0.08281605,-0.07622944,-0.23317504,0.04741395,0.01320128,0.0609445,-0.01199169,-0.06207977,-0.04417068,-0.07664093,0.04363108,-0.04887789,0.04833722,-0.01216682,-0.05081856,-0.01699465,-0.0424474,-0.02218416,-0.06070756,-0.00995597,-0.05402038,-0.08457571,-0.01662456,-0.07236797,-0.04903357,-0.00669642,-0.02891788,0.03913554,0.02438842,0.0349085,0.04236723,0.04450966,0.07003163,0.07015227,0.05532436,-0.22038248,0.09537825,0.00295073,0.02914267,-0.03268852,0.02762182,0.05825299,0.05146985,-0.00302322,-0.01680764,0.04260949,0.00937146,0.05119242,0.00610919,-0.02901776,-0.00278586,0.03570105,-0.01742077,0.00449782,0.04177951,-0.01805738,-0.09192731,-0.00049597,-0.05560185,-0.05394131,0.01774706,0.03198695,0.01725999,0.049474