"smart_blocks:cortex/parietal/inbox/2026/06/20/1158-session.md#Sessão Episódica: 2026-06-20 11:58#[decision] TTS Integration Phase 33 Initial Implementation: The initial part of PHASE-33 (TTS Integration) is complete. The system now has a robust foundation for audio generation, featuring a provider-based architecture that allows for easy expansion. By using build tags, the audio capabilities remain optional, ensuring the binary stays lean for non-audio users. The implementation of Kokoro and Qwen3 as native providers (via Python subprocesses) bridges the gap between high-performance ML models and the Go runtime. The next critical steps involve integrating these capabilities into the Gateway and Channel adapters to enable actual voice delivery to users.": {"path":null,"last_embed":{"hash":"11clhbv","at":1782088669716},"embeddings":{"TaylorAI/bge-micro-v2":{"vec":[-0.06654394,-0.01896358,0.02630135,-0.06306379,-0.03136412,0.02306146,-0.09508611,0.0223023,0.06143615,0.04441807,0.05390155,-0.07134914,0.00348193,0.05058372,0.05881383,0.00475167,0.04826498,-0.02387021,0.06356017,0.01485194,0.04551191,0.00578871,0.02334194,0.00847578,-0.00954274,0.06973738,-0.03694909,-0.03834966,-0.0211717,-0.23326901,0.04816905,-0.04734971,0.05134802,-0.06550297,-0.05288067,-0.01478303,-0.05496539,-0.00509443,-0.02362,0.06940628,-0.00401782,0.02876112,-0.01456852,-0.11189924,-0.04287189,-0.042481,-0.02658222,-0.01274701,-0.00964644,-0.03210685,-0.06508453,-0.01706868,0.0125892,-0.00143444,-0.04939424,0.05499025,0.06720418,0.09366915,0.04643913,0.07025609,0.0441884,-0.02879138,-0.19396663,0.11941321,0.01861798,0.09384767,-0.00496252,0.00217725,0.00342799,0.03612594,-0.06048571,0.00953637,0.03872496,0.00225325,-0.00283354,-0.02412689,0.09101165,0.00623,0.01515766,-0.03835478,0.02137845,0.01098139,0.00307777,-0.02640898,-0.05558349,-0.02019854,-0.02939516,-0.02679072,-0.09113353,0.01907299,-0.03802992,0.01095101,-0.01330308,-0.01593729,-0.02076116,-0.01593606,0.00482407,-0.02513143,-0.00038