"smart_blocks:cortex/parietal/inbox/2026/06/20/1158-session.md#Sessão Episódica: 2026-06-20 11:58#[discovery] Etraider Comprehensive System Architecture: The analysis of Etraider reveals a sophisticated \"Foundation\" layer designed for autonomous crypto trading. While the system has a robust architectural skeleton—including a real-time dashboard, a dedicated AI agent worker, and a shared type system—it is currently a signal-generation and analysis engine rather than a full trading bot. The separation of the API and Agent processes mirrors the conceptual split in OpenAlice, and the use of a shared type contract ensures consistency across the full stack.": {"path":null,"last_embed":{"hash":"9my05z","at":1782088669780},"embeddings":{"TaylorAI/bge-micro-v2":{"vec":[-0.06463479,-0.01955964,0.0189672,-0.01264416,0.00048609,-0.00814026,-0.00254668,-0.00849445,0.00620287,0.02637084,0.02411782,-0.04881305,0.00192356,0.05667692,0.01768583,0.01507117,-0.07477881,0.06042791,0.10916904,0.00278055,0.07017414,-0.03388123,0.00801875,-0.06649171,-0.0216371,0.06372678,-0.02953897,-0.06769956,-0.03965697,-0.21626206,0.03590122,-0.02671336,0.05604009,0.01659587,0.0242122,0.01270193,-0.07358222,0.01448324,-0.04401067,0.00299688,-0.03688452,0.00768842,0.03520419,0.03061163,0.01192982,-0.03728075,-0.05546196,-0.0097142,-0.06253087,-0.0475756,-0.00295573,-0.02566923,0.03200747,0.02971781,-0.02106662,0.05954805,0.04315431,0.0559945,0.02878511,0.07075316,0.080644,0.02730094,-0.15518844,0.10691721,0.0588734,0.08003944,-0.05080928,-0.00907271,0.03318642,0.01636348,0.02236515,-0.00472261,0.02057984,-0.04106478,0.0531451,0.0025482,0.03526552,-0.04347609,0.01222128,-0.05653297,-0.01583713,-0.01561088,-0.03008688,0.02760489,-0.07108276,0.00236359,0.02042163,-0.00040396,0.04220835,0.00265299,-0.0115611,0.06544192,-0.00836108,0.00200219,-0.05901441,-0.02474427,0.02279053,0.04156683,-0.02808678,0.14196779,-0.00223563,-0.01175209,0.01409425,-0.01710366,0.0406284,-0.02943229,0.00807911,-0.07244483,-0.