"smart_blocks:cortex/parietal/inbox/2026/06/20/1158-session.md#Sessão Episódica: 2026-06-20 11:58#[decision] TTS Integration Strategy: Hermes to Thoth: The project aims to fully integrate the Hermes TTS capabilities into Thoth. This involves moving away from the current HTTP bridge toward a native Go implementation. The architectural change requires updating the gateway delivery contracts to handle audio formats instead of just text, enabling voice responses on messaging platforms like WhatsApp and Telegram. The implementation will be gated by a build flag and include an automated voice model installation process.": {"path":null,"last_embed":{"hash":"1vsbkez","at":1782088670256},"embeddings":{"TaylorAI/bge-micro-v2":{"vec":[-0.05456965,0.00862888,0.00162969,-0.03443129,-0.04460271,-0.00422969,-0.06767121,0.01986517,0.02451814,0.010315,0.03361242,-0.0509074,0.01946668,0.05539158,0.08661423,0.00716395,0.03076515,-0.01998217,0.02718771,0.07253516,0.05736043,-0.01430709,0.02746053,-0.0000371,-0.00693234,0.03474391,-0.01130434,-0.0646315,0.00796712,-0.20740023,0.07934792,-0.04113718,0.00790138,-0.03356347,-0.03069022,0.01763564,-0.05313033,-0.05047065,-0.05426757,0.03572567,0.01143809,0.02759349,-0.00010955,-0.10128576,-0.04455737,-0.06622321,-0.03659618,-0.03876789,-0.05293516,-0.02965016,-0.01991234,-0.01831654,0.00398388,-0.01669183,0.00424379,0.05668077,0.04559056,0.08799227,0.01478736,0.0599564,0.04776119,-0.02167876,-0.19752042,0.10999878,0.0161439,0.05756503,-0.04269095,0.01978076,0.015456,0.07449601,-0.0640222,0.02050617,0.00825996,0.03525986,0.05871818,0.02576304,0.07034708,-0.03110685,0.00199406,-0.0402024,0.00385713,0.01193524,-0.02083195,-0.00004576,-0.01134085,-0.05823743,-0.04221183,-0.02876219,-0.0490426,-0.00548005,-0.07808371,-0.00194811,0.02518911,0.02063694,0.01062514,-0.03003519,-0.00353559,-0.02656119,-0.03857613,0.10984029,0.0085574,0.02753892,-0.01039358,-0.06184334,0.07345086,-0.05547339,-0.04812012,-0.08026938,-0.01022327,0.06599082,-0.03235221,-