"smart_blocks:cortex/parietal/inbox/2026/06/20/1158-session.md#Sessão Episódica: 2026-06-20 11:58#[feature] Implement user logout functionality: A logout feature has been implemented, allowing users to securely end their sessions. The `/api/auth/logout` endpoint, protected by JWT authentication, invalidates the current user's token. This is achieved by adding the token to a blocklist, preventing its future use and effectively logging the user out.": {"path":null,"last_embed":{"hash":"yocsqh","at":1782088670393},"embeddings":{"TaylorAI/bge-micro-v2":{"vec":[-0.04009155,0.00695378,-0.00980308,-0.10532843,-0.04913326,0.03839077,0.00832764,0.02071254,0.01805044,-0.00880348,-0.05340444,-0.0408537,-0.02554248,0.009006,0.0372219,-0.05133499,-0.0244629,0.01980967,-0.03065822,-0.00137961,0.05692715,-0.02596401,0.01474855,-0.06067851,-0.05052799,0.07642695,-0.05952306,-0.0684944,-0.00569014,-0.16619949,0.03177084,-0.05033313,-0.01913625,-0.05283304,-0.04116823,-0.08782019,-0.02278833,0.0229061,-0.02931416,0.03323468,0.04982825,0.06304148,-0.01502557,-0.06514262,-0.0548149,-0.02197783,-0.05798617,-0.04548715,-0.0154432,-0.03131852,0.06534141,0.02572319,-0.00453463,0.02901035,-0.00599504,-0.02475735,-0.0228139,0.00912286,-0.01933714,0.10805037,0.03516277,0.01161472,-0.17069758,0.10515425,-0.01971094,0.00075024,-0.03688716,0.01180418,0.03214593,0.06360077,-0.02424004,0.01267334,-0.01947401,0.00705385,0.02962095,-0.05286935,0.03943662,0.01712979,-0.04785345,-0.03846443,-0.03729817,0.00081642,0.04954914,-0.0209625,-0.02722269,-0.02269797,-0.01383509,-0.0384507,0.01473678,0.06473219,0.02089036,0.0531297,0.01414976,0.0524684,-0.01711958,-0.01438437,0.01733038,0.02522024,-0.10014945,0.15260173,-0.04530587,0.01121302,-0.02655873,-0.08024439,0.02699694,-0.01235754,0.01718665,0.00717774,-0.00538303,-0.03056949,0.01594208,-0.00400186,0.03856609,-0.02817052,0.00945965,-0.00538751,0.06421729,0.00940645,-0.00160796,-0.01001322,0.0260333,-0.00428985,0.01981045,-0.01285749,0.02977546,0.030491